SOURCE: https://github.com/rust-lang/reference.git/blob/master/src/attributes.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: grammar
CODE:
```
MetaItem ->
      SimplePath
    | SimplePath `=` Expression
    | SimplePath `(` MetaSeq? `)`

MetaSeq ->
    MetaItemInner ( `,` MetaItemInner )* `,`?

MetaItemInner ->
      MetaItem
    | Expression
```

