TITLE: Defining Macro Invocation Syntax in Rust
DESCRIPTION: Specifies the grammar for macro invocation in Rust, including the structure of DelimTokenTree and TokenTree.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rust-lang/reference.git/blob/master/src/macros.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: grammar
CODE:
```
MacroInvocation ->
    SimplePath `!` DelimTokenTree

DelimTokenTree ->
      `(` TokenTree* `)`
    | `[` TokenTree* `]`
    | `{` TokenTree* `}`

TokenTree ->
    Token _except [delimiters][lex.token.delim]_ | DelimTokenTree

MacroInvocationSemi ->
