TITLE: Required Explicit Registers with clobber_abi (Failing Example)
DESCRIPTION: Example showing that generic register class outputs are disallowed when using clobber_abi - all outputs must specify explicit registers to avoid conflicts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rust-lang/reference.git/blob/master/src/inline-assembly.md#2025-04-21_snippet_29

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
