TITLE: Defining Lifetime and Loop Label Grammar in Rust
DESCRIPTION: This grammar defines the syntax for lifetime parameters and loop labels in Rust, including raw lifetimes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rust-lang/reference.git/blob/master/src/tokens.md#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: grammar
CODE:
```
LIFETIME_TOKEN ->
      `'` IDENTIFIER_OR_KEYWORD _not immediately followed by `'`_
    | `'_` _not immediately followed by `'`_
    | RAW_LIFETIME

LIFETIME_OR_LABEL ->
      `'` NON_KEYWORD_IDENTIFIER _not immediately followed by `'`_
    | RAW_LIFETIME

RAW_LIFETIME ->
    `'r#` IDENTIFIER_OR_KEYWORD _except `crate`, `self`, `super`, `Self` and not immediately followed by `'`_

RESERVED_RAW_LIFETIME -> `'r#_` _not immediately followed by `'`_
```

